import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Hero } from '../hero'; @Component({ selector: 'app-hero-form', templateUrl: './hero-form.component.html', styleUrls: ['./hero-form.component.css'] }) export class HeroFormComponent { powers = ['Really Smart', 'Super Flexible', 'Super Hot', 'Weather Changer']; model = new Hero(18, 'Dr. IQ', this.powers[0], 'Chuck Overstreet'); submitted = false; onSubmit() { this.submitted = true; const myhero = new Hero(42, 'SkyDog', 'Fetch at any distance', 'leslie Rollover'); console.log('My hero is called ' + myhero.name); } newHero() { this.model = new Hero(42, '', ''); } }
